Tateyama Kurobe Alpine Route opened to the public today in Japan . 
  The 65ft high snow cavern is located on the winding track of Murodo in the region of Tateyama . 
  The route usually attracts a million visitors a year but numbers dropped to 910,000 last year . 
  The walled wonder is expected to rise to one million this year with the opening of a new line . 
 